# darwin.linux-builder writes these into its working dir (its SSH keypair and
# VM disk). Never commit them — keys/ holds a private key. Unanchored so they
# match wherever the builder is run from. Better still: run it from a dedicated
# dir outside the repo (see host-setup/linux-builder/README.md).
keys/
